<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.2) 0%, rgba(0,36,61,0.6) 50%), url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/301692/pexels-photo-301692.jpeg?w=940&h=650&dpr=2&auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb');">
  <div class="banner-content">
    <div class="text">
      <h1>Cocktails recipes</h1>
      <p>There's a drink for every mood or occasion. Find your favorite cocktail recipes below. <br>Or think outside the glass and try a brand new drink. Your new favorite could be a shake or stir away.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="cards">
    <% a, b = 0, 2 %>
    <% while @cocktails.size > b - 2 %>
      <div class='row'>
        <% @cocktails[a..b].each do |cocktail| %>
          <%= link_to cocktail_path(cocktail), class: "card-link" do %>
            <div class="card " style="background-image: linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.4) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.3) 50%), url('<%= cl_image_path cocktail.photo, height: 200, width: 300, crop: :fill %>');">
              <h4><%= cocktail.name %></h4>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <% a += 3 %>
      <% b += 3 %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

